bearerToken - Nested Action Documentation

Action Name: bearerToken

Action ID: d998c9a2-310f-46c1-b94e-6d4a088db559

Action Version: 0.0.0

Action OutputType: SecureString

Used in Workflow: HelloWorld

List of variables:

Variables NameVariables TypeVariables Description
vroURLstring
usernamestring
passwordSecureString

Script:

Script: 

// -----------------------------------------------------------------------
    // Build the  URL
    var uri = "https://" + vroURL + "/csp/gateway/am/api/login?access_token";
    // Import the  SSL certificate
    var ld = Config.getKeystores().getImportCAFromUrlAction();
    var model = ld.getModel();
        model.value = vroURL;
        error = ld.execute();

    //  Create REST call
        method = "POST"
        method = method.toUpperCase();

    //  Create a dynamic REST host
    var httpRestHost = null;
    var restHost = RESTHostManager.createHost("dynamicRequest");
        restHost.operationTimeout = 900;
        httpRestHost = RESTHostManager.createTransientHostFrom(restHost);
        httpRestHost.operationTimeout = 900;


        httpRestHost.url = uri;

        //BODY
    var requestBody = {
        "username": username,
        "password" : password
    }
    body = JSON.stringify(requestBody)

    var request = httpRestHost.createRequest(method,uri,body);
        request.setHeader("Content-Type", "application/json")
        request.setHeader("Accept", "application/json")
        response = request.execute();
    var jsonResponse = JSON.parse(response.contentAsString)

        refresh_token = jsonResponse["refresh_token"]


// -----------------------------------------------------------------------


    // Build the  URL
    var uri = "https://" + vroURL + "/iaas/api/login";
    // Import the  SSL certificate
    var ld = Config.getKeystores().getImportCAFromUrlAction();
    var model = ld.getModel();
        model.value = vroURL;
        error = ld.execute();

    //  Create REST call
        method = "POST"
        method = method.toUpperCase();

    //  Create a dynamic REST host
    var httpRestHost = null;
    var restHost = RESTHostManager.createHost("dynamicRequest");
        restHost.operationTimeout = 900;
        httpRestHost = RESTHostManager.createTransientHostFrom(restHost);
        httpRestHost.operationTimeout = 900;


        httpRestHost.url = uri;

        //BODY
    var requestBody = {
        "refreshToken": refresh_token
    }
    body = JSON.stringify(requestBody)

    var request = httpRestHost.createRequest(method,uri,body);
        request.setHeader("Content-Type", "application/json")
        request.setHeader("Accept", "application/json")
        response = request.execute();
    var jsonResponse = JSON.parse(response.contentAsString)

        bearerToken = jsonResponse["token"]

    return bearerToken
